F5:_*0.5 Ab5:_*0.5 C6:_*1 F5:_*0.5 Ab5:_*0.5 C6:_*1
F5:_*0.5 Ab5:_*0.5 C6:_*0.5 Eb6:_*0.5 C6:_*1 Eb6:_*1
Eb6:_*1 C6:_*1 Eb6:_*1 C6:_*1
Ab5:_*0.5 C6:_*0.5 Eb6:_*1 Ab5:_*0.5 C6:_*0.5 Eb6:_*1
F5:_*0.5 Ab5:_*0.5 C6:_*0.5 Eb6:_*0.5 C6:_*0.5 Ab5:_*0.5 Eb6:_*1
Eb6:_*4

